# Reactbits Component Locations

This rule documents the installation locations for components fetched from `https://reactbits.dev/ts/tailwind` using `npx jsrepo init`.

- **Animations**: Components related to animations are located in [./src/Animations](mdc:src/Animations)
- **Backgrounds**: Components for backgrounds are located in [./src/Backgrounds](mdc:src/Backgrounds)
- **Components**: General components are located in [./src/Components](mdc:src/Components)
- **TextAnimations**: Components for text animations are located in [./src/TextAnimations](mdc:src/TextAnimations)

Refer to these directories when working with the installed reactbits.dev components.
